sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as Resources List Page
    participant LW as Livewire Component
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open resources list
    UI->>LW: Initial request
    LW->>DB: Query resources with translation/media relations
    DB-->>LW: Paginated resources
    LW-->>UI: Render table and filters

    User->>UI: Search/filter/date/paginate
    UI->>LW: Update bound properties
    LW->>DB: Re-query with conditions
    DB-->>LW: Updated paginated result
    LW-->>UI: Re-render list

    User->>UI: Delete resource
    UI->>LW: deleteResource(id)
    LW->>DB: Delete translations/media/resource rows
    DB-->>LW: Deleted
    LW-->>UI: Success toast + refresh
